+#### Format embedded GQL in template literal statements (#16064 by @keithlayne)
+
+<!-- prettier-ignore -->
+```jsx
+// Input
+/* GraphQL */ `
+  query foo { id }
+`;
+
+// Prettier stable
+/* GraphQL */ `
+  query foo { id }
+`;
+
+// Prettier main
+/* GraphQL */ `
+  query foo {
+    id
+  }
+`;
+```
